Japan Foundation, in collaboration with The National Association of Business Ethics (NABE) presents 'Power & Walk', a carnival of Business Ethics conducted in 28 Japanese cities.

The National Association for Business Ethics (NABE) holds its first carnival in Fiji by joining forces with the Japan Foundation Tokyo Seminar and Training Centre. It is visiting the 19 cities/countries of the Pacific Rim in the following order:
